Saqib Sharif: AIC - Activity Data & Scan Summary not Visible

posted in SWAT Teams: Product Discussions, PM Q&A, Feedback / NEA Core on Friday, 4 October 2024 5:18 pm
What We've Learned Updated: The customer is using EOL and EOS version of StealthAudit and AIC. When they view scan summary in AIC, no data is displayed.
Next Steps Updated: Customer has been recommended to upgrade after confirmation from the dev team.
